<topic id='element_cancer_care_spell_delay_reason_comment__referral_to_treatment_.description'>
  <title>Description</title>
  <titlealts>
    <searchtitle>Data Element: CANCER CARE SPELL DELAY REASON COMMENT (REFERRAL TO TREATMENT) - Description</searchtitle>
  </titlealts>
  <body>
  <div>
      <p>
         <xref outputclass="element"
               keyref="element_cancer_care_spell_delay_reason_comment__referral_to_treatment_">CANCER CARE SPELL DELAY REASON COMMENT (REFERRAL TO TREATMENT)</xref>
 is the same as attribute 
              <xref outputclass="attribute"
               keyref="attribute_cancer_care_spell_delay_reason_comment">CANCER CARE SPELL DELAY REASON COMMENT</xref>.        </p>
      <p>
         <xref outputclass="element"
               keyref="element_cancer_care_spell_delay_reason_comment__referral_to_treatment_">CANCER CARE SPELL DELAY REASON COMMENT (REFERRAL TO TREATMENT)</xref>
 is the free text comment field to describe why a 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_cancer_care_spell_delay">Cancer Care Spell Delay</xref>
 occurred:        </p>
      <ul>
         <li>
            <div>
               <p>
between the 
                                <xref outputclass="element"
                        keyref="element_cancer_referral_to_treatment_period_start_date">CANCER REFERRAL TO TREATMENT PERIOD START DATE</xref>
 and 
                                <xref outputclass="element" keyref="element_treatment_start_date__cancer_">TREATMENT START DATE (CANCER)</xref>
 and                    </p>
            </div>
         </li>
         <li>
            <div>
               <p>
less any adjustments recorded by 
                                <xref outputclass="element"
                        keyref="element_waiting_time_adjustment__first_seen_">WAITING TIME ADJUSTMENT (FIRST SEEN)</xref>
 and 
                                <xref outputclass="element"
                        keyref="element_waiting_time_adjustment__treatment_">WAITING TIME ADJUSTMENT (TREATMENT)</xref>
 and                    </p>
            </div>
         </li>
         <li>
            <div>
               <p>
where the 
                                <xref outputclass="attribute"
                        keyref="attribute_cancer_care_spell_delay_reason">CANCER CARE SPELL DELAY REASON</xref>
 is National Code 
                                <i>'Other reason (not listed)'</i>
 or any additional supporting information is required.                    </p>
            </div>
         </li>
      </ul>
  </div>
</body>
